  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bcd ; \u0b85\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Squid season on Gulf of Mannar coast; Pamban Pass is exported to Arab countries",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the season of tube squid for export to Arab countries has started, fishermen are happy with the high availability of pampan trawler fishing in the Gulf of Mannar region.",
        "More than 90 trawlers from Pampan South Fishing Port went to the Gulf of Mannar to fish and a large number of tube squid were caught in the deep sea.",
        "Anglers call it tube pass because it looks like a bicycle tube.",
        "It is a type of nightmare. Up to one foot in length. It also has another name as needle pass.",
        "These squid can swim at a speed of 70 kilometers per hour.",
        "At present, it is sold at Rs.200 to Rs.250 per kg.",
        "It is sent to Kochi by traders at Pampan fishing port and from there it is exported to Arab countries.",
        "This type of squid has the ability to escape from enemies by releasing a black liquid to escape from larger fish."
      ],
